      <bioghist id="aspace_9a2235ebdb03027901ec9b2f5591a825">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Paul Mellon Fellowship is offered to an unmarried member of the Senior Class in Yale College for study at Clare College, Cambridge, for the academic year.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_04a86b543e781da5ca0e468b877530c8">
